Taco Bell: No Drive Worth Dying For
Construction crew watches in disbelief as determined customer ignores EVERY warning sign and drives straight into fresh concrete for a burrito fix. Car gets stuck, concrete ruined, and crew forced to start over. The lengths people go for fast food! #ConcreteNightmare #ConstructionFails #bluecollar
